                        		<td width="100%" style="text-align:center;font-size:10pt;"><b>Best Before : 180 Days from the Date of Mfg.</b></td>
                        	</tr>
                        </table>
                    </t>
                    <t t-if="o.production_id.label_type == 'export_us'">
